OL,5, One of Britain's largest energy        
OL,6, suppliers has apologised after it      
OL,7, advised customers they could cuddle    
OL,8, pets and eat porridge to stay warm.    
OL,10,FOvo Energy said it was "embarrassed"   
OL,11,Fafter a link to a blog "containing     
OL,12,Fenergy-saving tips" was sent to its SSE
OL,13,Fcustomers, a brand which it owns.      
OL,15,FThe company said it had removed the    
OL,16,Fblog so it could "update it" with "more
OL,17,Fmeaningful information for customers". 
OL,19,FIt comes after concerns over the cost  
OL,20,Fof living amid rising energy bills.    
